docs_page_main_description: PUMP TUBE is the first dedicated platform for the fair launch and trading of  project token.PUMP TUBE offers creators an accessible, low-cost way to launch their own project token in a secure and user-friendly environment. This innovative platform will elevate user engagement and promote a more autonomous trading experience.
docs_page_sub_description: PUMP TUBE combines user-friendliness, fairness, and accountability. The operational mechanism streamlines token issuance and trading, allowing users to easily browse and select their preferred project token on the platform. A joint curve pricing mechanism provides direct and transparent access to token purchases. PUMP TUBE also offers flexible trading options, allowing users to sell their tokens whenever they choose.
how_to_participate_step_1_desc: Users first explore project token on the PUMP TUBE platform and pick out the ones that grab their interest to embark on a personalized cryptocurrency journey.
how_to_participate_step_2_desc: Users buy tokens using PUMP TUBE’s  Iceberg Curve mechanism, which offers them a user-friendly purchasing process and easy entry into the coin market.
how_to_participate_step_3_desc: PUMP TUBE offers flexible trading options for users to sell their tokens at any time, whether to lock in profits or cut losses.
how_to_participate_step_4_desc: As community engagement and purchases increase, the market value of project token is expected to shoot up, potentially reaching 100% of the  Iceberg Curve.
create_a_liquidity_and_burn_mechanism_te: Create a liquidity and burn mechanism
how_to_participate_step_5_desc: Once the  Iceberg Curve completes, around $100,000 worth of tubeUSD in liquidity support will be automatically deposited into TubeSwap and burned.
how_to_launch_page_desc: Launching your project on PUMP TUBE is easy–simply provide the essential details to complete the token issuance. You can set pre-buy measures against bot purchases to ensure full benefits for all genuine participants.
laucnh_step_2_text: Before launching, developers can buy a portion of their token supply in the same transaction to safeguard against snipers.
laucnh_step_3_text: Once this is done, simply confirm the transaction, and you're ready to go.
